    IJspUI<C>, IUI<C>, IUIList<C,​IJspUIContext,​UITab>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    UITabs
    public class UITabs<C extends IJspUIContext>
extends AbstractPropertyUIList<C,​IJspUIContext,​UITab>
    Convenient holder of tabs list.

    Returns items that are both enabled by property configuration (See AbstractPropertyUI.ENABLED_PROP_SUFFIX and not skipped from (optional) validation JSP (See AbstractPropertyUI.isEnabled(HttpServletRequest)).

    Since:
    esn-6.2
    Author:
    Sylvain Devaux
